(modified from 
<bibRefCitation id="F6414B51D458B524FEA7B06B617C8F7E" author="Belokobylskij, S. A." box="[330,560,1303,1329]" pageId="1" pageNumber="41" pagination="1019 - 1026" refId="ref5674" refString="Belokobylskij, S. A. (1984) On the division of the tribe Exothecini s. l. (Hymenoptera, Braconidae) in two with the description of a new genus and subgenus. Zoologicheskii Zhurnal, 63, 1019 - 1026. [in Russian with English summary]" type="journal article" year="1984">Belokobylskij, 1984</bibRefCitation>
